en_211511_0	The National Water Supply and Drainage Board stated that a water cut will be imposed on several areas in Colombo today.
en_211511_1	Accordingly, the water supply will be suspended for Colombo 13, 14 and 15 starting from 9.00 a.m. today until 3.00 p.m. on Sunday.
en_211511_2	In addition to this, water will be supplied under low pressure for Fort and Pettah areas.
